{
  "texts": [
    "Similar such sets [ACC + 19] have also been used in major FHE libraries as a lookup table to inform default parameters.",
    "We will mention this further in Section 5.4.",
    "Efforts have also explored frameworks or formulas as alternatives to lookup tables for selecting FHE parameters, e.g.",
    "[BBB + 23, MML + 23, KMR24].",
    "The remainder of this document is organized as follows."
  ]
}